replyContent:
It is a common Airpods problem search on google "airpods absolute volume" or

Solution 1:
Go to your bluetooth settings, click the three dots and turn off media volume sync

Solution 2:
Go into developer settings and disable absolute volume for bluetooth

Also: Make sure you don't turn on listen assist then play music while it is still switched on.
